products.title: CyberHog
products.description: A hedgehog with cybernetic enhancements and neon-glowing quills. Its body is a blend of organic and mechanical parts.

products.title: Solarwhale
products.description: A small whale that absorbs sunlight through its skin. Its smooth, reflective body glows with stored solar energy.

products.title: Snakeling
products.description: A snake with the legs of a spider. Its long, serpentine body is supported by multiple, spindly legs.

products.title: Froggle
products.description: A frog with the playful nature of a beagle. It has the body of a frog and the ears and tail of a beagle.

products.title: Penguicorn
products.description: A penguin with a unicorn horn. It has a sleek black and white body with a magical, spiraled horn.

products.title: Octopug
products.description: A pug with eight tentacle legs. It has a cute pug face and flexible, multifunctional tentacles.
